rows.label: tlk42360111_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Don't talk to me while
I'm piloting, mo!

rows.label: tlk42360111_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The ether energy generated from
the Cloud Sea is essential for
a Divine Beast to fly, mo!

rows.label: tlk42360111_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But if you lower the altitude too
much, you'll be attacked by the
monsters lurking within, mo.

rows.label: tlk42360111_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Maintaining an altitude that allows
for speed while making it difficult
for monsters to attack...

rows.label: tlk42360111_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Piloting requires the technique
to make these delicate
movements possible, mo!
